Shaftesbury Appoints Christoper Ward as Finance Director

-- B y   R o s s   L a r s e n
-- 
2011-10-03T06:05:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/shaftesbury-appoints-christoper-ward-as-finance-director.html
Sheftesbury Plc said  Christopher Ward 
has been appointed finance director. As previously announced,
Brian Bickell took over as chief executive officer and Jonathan
Lane became deputy chairman as of Oct. 1.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ross Larsen in London at 
